Title: The Path to Fitness
Text: Next on my journey for a Personal Defense Permit is to locate the Gramados Gymnasium, where I'll undergo self-defense training. It's time to find the gym and see what challenges await me.
CompleteText: I've arrived at the Gramados Gymnasium, the training ground for many aspiring defenders. Stepping through its doors, I feel ready to tackle the physical challenges that will surely test my resolve.
